<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg von Murach zu Flügelsberg, Pfleger, und Kelheim</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Mitteilung des Geständnisses des zu Kelheim gefangenen H. Wagenhals über den Mord an Hermann Sensenschmied, Bürger zu Nürnberg, kündigt die Freunde des Ermordeten an und bittet um deren Unterstützung wegen gerichtlicher Belangung Wagenhals'. Im beigefügten Zettel wird die Zahlung des Botenlohns bestätigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_566" id="282r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_566_r1l1"><expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Murah<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>flügelſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> . <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l2">dem Rate der Stat ʒu kelheım </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_566_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des knechts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l4"> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> genant <expan cert="unknown">h</expan>  wagenhalls der Jn <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> fenknuſſ . <expan>bekan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l5">daʒ er ſelbfımft <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> den <expan>h<ex>er</ex>man</expan> ſenſenſmid <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>ſchult</expan> der = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l6">mördt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / Des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l8">fleıſʒ / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_566_r1l7">wıſſen </ab></add> / daʒ wır das <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>ſelıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l9"><expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> alſo ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / dıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu eẅch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l10"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> vnd den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>nachʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> als darcʒu gebürt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l11"><expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eẅr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l12">vnd guten <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> als etc / vnd wır den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l13"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns auch tun <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> das wellen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_566_r1l16">Cettula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l15">Auch <expan>l<ex>ıeben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> haben wır dıſem <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> das bottenlon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_566_r1l17">geben </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_566" id="282r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Gö̈rg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Murah<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>Flügelsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>, und dem rate der stat zu Kelheim
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des knechts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> genant <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Wagenhalls, der in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fenknuss
                                <expan>bekan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> hat, daz er selbfünft
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, den <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan>
                        Sensensmid, <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>schult</expan> dermördt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., des
                            <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<add>wissen</add>, daz wir das <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> also zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, die <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                        ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> und den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>nachzukome<ex>n</ex></expan>, als darczu gebürt;
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        und guten <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> in den
                            <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>, als
                        etc. und wir den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns auch tun
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>; das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula: Auch <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> haben wir disem <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> das bottenlon geben. </ab>
</div>
